Aku akan keluar dan memancing mereka.

189
00:16:37,727 --> 00:16:40,063
- Kalian harus lari.
- Aku tak bisa.

190
00:16:40,146 --> 00:16:42,523
- Sersan Kepala Pyo.
- Aku tak mau dengar.

191
00:16:43,358 --> 00:16:44,484
Semoga kalian selamat.

192
00:16:44,984 --> 00:16:46,611
