01:09:32,293 --> 01:09:33,544
Ada apa?

929
01:09:37,590 --> 01:09:38,674
Yoon Se-ri.

930
01:09:40,801 --> 01:09:42,428
Bagaimana keadaannya?

931
01:09:42,761 --> 01:09:44,346
Dia di unit perawatan intensif.

932
01:09:45,639 --> 01:09:48,058
Dia mengalami sepsis,
sebagai efek samping operasi.

933
01:09:49,560 --> 01:09:52,104
Kenapa perlakukan dia dengan kasar

934
01:09:53,063 --> 01:09:54,481
jika kau tak tahan juga?

935
01:10:20,966 --> 01:10:22,301
Terima kasih.

936
01:10:24,178 --> 01:10:25,554
Aku pergi dahulu.

937
01:10:31,310 --> 01:10:32,269
Jaga kesehatanmu.

938
01:10:37,566 --> 01:10:39,652
Jangan sampai sakit.

939
01:12:05,612 --> 01:12:07,740
<i>Kamerad Gu Seung-jun.</i>

940
01:12:08,323 --> 01:12:10,159
<i>Jika kau tak ikut kami sekarang,</i>

941
01:12:10,617 --> 01:12:12,870
<i>akan kami bawa wanita ini.</i>

942
01:12:13,829 --> 01:12:14,997
<i>Lepaskan aku!</i>

943
01:12:17,916 --> 01:12:21,253
Kau bicara dengan orang yang salah.

944
01:12:21,336 --> 01:12:23,380
Aku tak ada hubungannya dengan wanita itu.

945
01:12:23,464 --> 01:12:26,633
Aku tak peduli jika kalian
mau bawa dia atau tidak.

946
01:12:26,717 --> 01:12:28,302
<i>Begitukah?</i>

947
01:12:28,969 --> 01:12:31,680
<i>Kau tak peduli jika kami membunuhnya.</i>

948
01:12:32,890 --> 01:12:34,141
Aku tak peduli.

949
01:12:34,433 --> 01:12:37,227
<i>Mari kita bicara lagi
setelah kami membunuhnya.</i>

950
01:12:37,728 --> 01:12:38,854
Tunggu.

951
01:12:40,856 --> 01:12:42,900
Kenapa mau membunuh wanita tak bersalah?

952
01:12:42,983 --> 01:12:45,110
Keluarganya sangat berkuasa.

953
01:12:45,194 --> 01:12:48,155
Kalian bisa dihabisi
jika berani menyentuhnya.

954
01:12:48,238 --> 01:12:51,950
<i>Kami tak takut pada hal semacam itu.</i>

955
01:12:52,451 --> 01:12:54,244
<i>Waktumu hanya satu jam.</i>

956
01:12:54,328 --> 01:12:56,789
<i>Datanglah ke alamat
dari pesan singkat ini.</i>

957
01:12:56,872 --> 01:12:58,624
<i>Jika tidak, wanita ini mati.</i>

958
01:12:59,458 --> 01:13:01,293
<i>Jika bawa bantuan, wanita ini mati.</i>

959
01:13:01,502 --> 01:13:02,878
<i>Aku yakin kau pasti paham.</i>

960
01:13:04,963 --> 01:13:06,965
Halo?

961
01:13:10,177 --> 01:13:11,470
<font color="#00ffff">WAKTU NAIK PESAWAT, 11.30</font>

962
01:13:27,861 --> 01:13:29,905
Pasangkan infus lagi,

963
01:13:29,988 --> 01:13:31,782
dan periksa organ vitalnya lagi.

964
01:13:32,533 --> 01:13:34,701
Bu Yoon.

965
01:13:41,291 --> 01:13:42,709
<i>Aku bermimpi.</i>

966
01:13:52,302 --> 01:13:54,304
Bu Yoon, jadwalmu selanjutnya,

967
01:13:54,388 --> 01:13:56,223
uji coba pakaian olahraga ekstrem.

968
01:13:56,306 --> 01:13:58,934
Sungguh akan kau coba sendiri?

969
01:14:00,018 --> 01:14:01,186
Maksudku, paralayangnya.

970
01:14:01,270 --> 01:14:03,647
<font color="#00ffff">BAJU OLAHRAGA PILIHAN SE-RI</font>

971
01:14:04,314 --> 01:14:06,191
<i>Di dalam mimpiku,</i>

972
01:14:06,775 --> 01:14:10,529
<i>aku kembali ke hari kecelakaan itu.</i>

973
01:14:10,612 --> 01:14:12,072
Bu Yoon?

974
01:14:41,894 --> 01:14:43,812
<i>Di dalam mimpiku,</i>

975
01:14:44,730 --> 01:14:47,399
<i>aku tahu segalanya.</i>

976
01:14:48,233 --> 01:14:50,027
<i>Aku tahu</i>

977
01:14:50,444 --> 01:14:52,446
<i>kecelakaan apa yang akan kualami</i>

978
01:14:53,238 --> 01:14:55,532
<i>dan di mana aku akan terdampar.</i>

979
01:14:56,033 --> 01:14:57,826
<i>Aku tahu akan bertemu siapa</i>

980
01:14:58,869 --> 01:15:02,039
<i>dan pengalaman menakutkan dan sulit
yang akan kualami.</i>

981
01:15:03,165 --> 01:15:04,541
<i>Aku juga tahu</i>

982
01:15:05,626 --> 01:15:07,794
<i>hari ini akan segera berakhir.</i>

983
01:15:08,545 --> 01:15:09,880
<i>Aku sudah tahu segalanya.</i>

984
01:15:10,380 --> 01:15:11,590
Apa?

985
01:15:12,633 --> 01:15:13,759
Baiklah.

986
01:15:18,764 --> 01:15:20,140
Yoon Se-ri

987
01:15:21,516 --> 01:15:22,851
dalam kondisi kritis.

988
01:15:34,821 --> 01:15:35,781
<font color="#00ffff">RUANG TUNGGU</font>

989
01:16:17,072 --> 01:16:18,156
<font color="#00ffff">WAKTU NAIK PESAWAT, 11.30</font>

990
01:17:23,055 --> 01:17:24,723
Jangan bergerak.

991
01:17:40,364 --> 01:17:41,823
Gu Seung-jun!

992
01:17:46,620 --> 01:17:48,622
Seo Dan, jangan khawatir.

993
01:17:49,331 --> 01:17:51,917
Aku belajar menembak di Selatan.

994
01:18:18,360 --> 01:18:19,736
Gu Seung-jun!

995
01:18:32,707 --> 01:18:34,126
<i>Aku salah.</i>

996
01:18:35,293 --> 01:18:36,837
<i>Saat aku mati,</i>

997
01:18:37,295 --> 01:18:40,382
<i>ada seseorang yang menangisiku.</i>

998
01:18:41,383 --> 01:18:43,176
<i>Fakta bahwa kaulah orangnya</i>

999
01:18:44,386 --> 01:18:47,597
<i>membuatku sedih dan bahagia.</i>

1000
01:18:57,774 --> 01:19:00,152
<i>Di akhir mimpi panjang itu,</i>

1001
01:19:00,569 --> 01:19:04,114
<i>akhirnya aku mengambil keputusan.</i>

1002
01:19:28,054 --> 01:19:30,140
Anginnya cukup kuat.

1003
01:19:30,223 --> 01:19:32,642
Kami sudah periksa ramalan cuaca,
kau tak apa-apa?

1004
01:19:32,726 --> 01:19:35,228
Pak Hong. Kenapa angin bertiup?

1005
01:19:35,312 --> 01:19:37,314
Entahlah.

1006
01:19:39,566 --> 01:19:41,067
Angin bertiup untuk bergerak.

1007
01:19:45,530 --> 01:19:47,699
Angin bertiup untuk bergerak,

1008
01:19:48,783 --> 01:19:50,911
bukan tetap diam.

1009
01:19:53,121 --> 01:19:55,165
Angin harus tetap bergerak

1010
01:19:56,082 --> 01:19:57,918
agar aku bisa terbang.

1011
01:20:00,378 --> 01:20:02,172
<i>Demi bisa menemui dirimu,</i>

1012
01:20:02,881 --> 01:20:05,467
<i>aku ambil keputusan
untuk mengulangi semua momen itu</i>

1013
01:20:06,468 --> 01:20:08,470
<i>dari awal.</i>

1014
01:20:10,430 --> 01:20:12,098
Berikan epinefrin melalui infus.

1015
01:20:12,182 --> 01:20:13,600
Baik, Dok.

1016
01:20:14,643 --> 01:20:16,561
<i>Walau waktu kuputar kembali</i>

1017
01:20:17,312 --> 01:20:18,855
<i>seratus kali...</i>

1018
01:20:19,606 --> 01:20:21,566
<i>Jika aku bisa memutar balik waktu...</i>

1019
01:20:22,067 --> 01:20:23,902
<i>Andai aku bisa,</i>

1020
01:20:24,653 --> 01:20:26,780
<i>aku tak mau menemuimu.</i>

1021
01:20:27,155 --> 01:20:28,865
<i>Kau takkan bisa kenal diriku.</i>

1022
01:20:30,200 --> 01:20:33,161
<i>Maka kau akan aman dan bahagia.</i>

1023
01:20:33,995 --> 01:20:35,497
<i>Andai aku bisa melakukannya...</i>

1024
01:20:36,456 --> 01:20:38,166
<i>Aku akan bertemu denganmu lagi.</i>

1025
01:20:39,000 --> 01:20:40,585
<i>Aku akan kenal denganmu</i>

1026
01:20:41,294 --> 01:20:42,837
<i>dan jatuh cinta.</i>

1027
01:20:43,755 --> 01:20:46,591
<i>Aku tahu itu pilihan</i>

1028
01:20:47,926 --> 01:20:49,469
<i>yang berbahaya dan menyedihkan.</i>

1029
01:20:49,553 --> 01:20:51,221
<font color="#00ffff">AMBULANS</font>

1030
01:20:57,435 --> 01:21:00,939
<i>Jika salah satu dari kita harus mati,</i>

1031
01:21:01,356 --> 01:21:03,441
<i>dan yang lain tetap hidup...</i>

1032
01:21:05,485 --> 01:21:07,779
<i>Jika memang itu takdirnya,</i>

1033
01:21:08,738 --> 01:21:10,657
<i>maka wajar saja</i>

1034
01:21:11,032 --> 01:21:14,494
<i>aku mati dan kau tetap hidup.</i>

1035
01:21:16,538 --> 01:21:18,164
<i>Wajar saja.</i>

1036
01:21:26,423 --> 01:21:28,049
<i>Aku bahagia</i>

1037
01:21:29,759 --> 01:21:32,721
<i>mengambil keputusan itu, Ri Jeong Hyeok.</i>

1038
01:22:46,336 --> 01:22:47,587
Itu saja?

1039
01:22:48,505 --> 01:22:51,174
Para psikolog menganalisis

1040
01:22:51,257 --> 01:22:53,009
pola sikap Ri Jeong Hyeok

1041
01:22:53,093 --> 01:22:54,552
terhadap Yoon Se-ri.

1042
01:22:54,678 --> 01:22:56,221
Ini hasilnya.

1043
01:22:56,304 --> 01:22:57,305
Baiklah.

1044
01:22:57,389 --> 01:22:58,640
Ini.

1045
01:23:02,977 --> 01:23:05,647
<i>Seperti yang terlihat,
saat Jeong Hyeok bersama Se-ri,</i>

1046
01:23:05,730 --> 01:23:07,023
<i>pusat batang tubuhnya</i>

1047
01:23:07,107 --> 01:23:09,442
<i>menghadap 90 persen ke arah Yoon Se-ri.</i>

1048
01:23:11,152 --> 01:23:15,532
<i>Ri Jeong Hyeok mengikuti gerakannya
tanpa sadar berulang kali.</i>

1049
01:23:23,123 --> 01:23:24,624
<i>Saat ada pria mendekatinya,</i>

1050
01:23:24,708 --> 01:23:27,168
<i>dia mengalihkan perhatian
dan pergerakan Yoon Se-ri</i>

1051
01:23:27,252 --> 01:23:28,586
<i>berulang kali.</i>

1052
01:23:32,382 --> 01:23:34,300
Ahli psikolog, Profesor Oh Hyeong-sim,

1053
01:23:34,384 --> 01:23:36,261
menganalisis bahwa ini sikap umum

1054
01:23:36,886 --> 01:23:40,974
- pada pria yang jatuh cinta.
- Kau butuh analisis untuk tahu itu?

1055
01:23:42,142 --> 01:23:43,935
Itu sudah terlihat jelas.

1056
01:23:45,562 --> 01:23:46,855
Yang benar saja.

